### Smart Campus Parking API - Test File
### Install VS Code extension: humao.rest-client
### Then click "Send Request" on any endpoint below

@base = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── Health Check ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/health

### ─── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login as Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@campus.edu",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login as Staff
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "staff@campus.edu",
  "password": "staff123"
}

### Login as User
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rahul@campus.edu",
  "password": "user123"
}

### Register new user
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@campus.edu",
  "password": "test123",
  "vehicleNumber": "UP32XY9999",
  "phone": "9999999999"
}

### Get Current User
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── SLOTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all slots
GET {{base}}/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get available slots only
GET {{base}}/slots/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by zone
GET {{base}}/slots?zone=A&status=available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── BOOKINGS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create booking (replace slotId with actual ID from slots)
POST {{base}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": "REPLACE_WITH_SLOT_ID",
  "vehicleNumber": "UP32AB1234",
  "estimatedDuration": 2
}

### My bookings
GET {{base}}/bookings/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Active booking
GET {{base}}/bookings/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── STAFF ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Active bookings (Staff/Admin)
GET {{base}}/staff/active-bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search vehicle
GET {{base}}/staff/search?vehicleNumber=UP32AB1234
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check in (replace bookingId)
POST {{base}}/staff/checkin/BOOKING_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check out (replace bookingId)
POST {{base}}/staff/checkout/BOOKING_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "cash"
}

### ─── ADMIN ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Dashboard
GET {{base}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All users
GET {{base}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Revenue (period: week / month / year)
GET {{base}}/admin/revenue?period=month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
